</code></pre> Output: The Hatching a Plan first objective is to find where the eggs are being incubated <pre><code>/echo The ${Task[hatch]} first objective status is ${Task[hatch].Objective[1].Status}
</code></pre> Output: The Hatching a Plan first objective status is 0/1 <pre><code>/echo The ${Task[hatch]} first objective should be completed in ${Task[hatch].Objective[1].Zone}
